snippet.title: Danganronpa: LIVe or Die - full playthrough (no commentary) - #01 Prologue
snippet.description:
Danganronpa: LIVe or Die is a Fangan (Danganronpa fan game) created by Aru & Raven in RPG Maker 2003. Prologue and chapter 1 are available for download for free at itch.io.

Download link: https://darkraven616.itch.io/danganronpa-live-or-die
Twitter: https://twitter.com/DR_LIVeordie
Discord: https://discord.gg/Y4TuKmqst6
